parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause a significant loss of braking power, leading to extended stopping distances, accidents, and potentially life-threatening situations.
symptoms: Soft or mushy brake pedal
brake pedal travels to the floor
long stopping distances
brakes locking up or pulling to one side
near-miss accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of other brake system components can cause similar issues, including loss of braking power, extended stopping distances, and accidents.
symptoms: Soft or mushy brake pedal
brake pedal travels to the floor
long stopping distances
brakes locking up or pulling to one side
near-miss accidents
vibration when depressing the brake pedal
Pre-Collision malfunction warning light illumination.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders under load
especially uphill or from a stop
the transmission hunts for gears during shifts
clanking and metallic clicking sounds come from the bell housing
transmission casing and bell housing radiate excessive heat
the vehicle's average mileage drops
and the transmission pops out of gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission engagement and disengagement issues can cause the vehicle to roll backwards on hills, leading to accidents or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls backwards on hills when the "Hill Assist" disengages
the transmission hesitates or stalls when accelerating
and the vehicle's engine hesitates or stalls when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Airbag Deployment in Crash Situations
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in crash situations can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the vehicle's safety features are not functioning as intended.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy despite significant frontal or side impact
airbag warning light is illuminated on the dashboard
notification of airbag malfunction through vehicle's app or dealership
seatbelts do not lock or function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the vehicle can lead to loss of control, accidents, and potentially cause injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls at random times and speeds
all engine lights turn on
and the vehicle shuts off. The driver needs to roll to a safe spot
put the vehicle in park
turn off the engine
and then turn it back on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The blurry and unreliable exterior cameras can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when reversing or parking, as the driver may not be able to observe obstacles or hazards.
symptoms: The exterior cameras produce blurry images
flare up in direct sunlight
and are unreliable for safe viewing behind the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can lead to loss of control, accidents, and potentially cause injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates on its own while the brake pedal is depressed
the steering wheel locks
and the driver is unable to stop the vehicle.
